OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFurther rain
OL,6,Fspreads north this evening, heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. Turning showery but winds
OL,8,Fincreasing to gale or severe gale for
OL,9,Fa time. Winds easing overnight with
OL,10,Fskies clearing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,13,Fshowers through the day, these heavy
OL,14,Fat times, and wintry over the hills.
OL,15,FShowers more frequent for a time in
OL,16,Fthe morning. Blustery winds at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
